V0207_01_00_00_0.text: You can't elude the long arm of the law!

V0207_01_00_01_0.text: You really think I'd lose to you?

V0207_01_00_02_0.text:
What's your alibi for challenging me?
Temporary insanity?

V0207_01_00_03_0.text: You can never outrun Sector Security!

V0207_01_00_04_0.text: I'm taking you down to the brig for questioning!

V0207_01_00_05_0.text:
It's MY duty to protect New Domino City!
Not you vagrants!

V0207_01_00_06_0.text: I won't take it easy just cuz you're a juvie, Leo!

V0207_01_00_07_0.text:
Those kids don't have the authority to keep the peace!
I do!

V0207_03_00_00_0.text: I'll chase ya down to the ends of the earth!

V0207_05_00_00_0.text: Sector Security will protect the citizens at all costs!

V0207_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my face-down card!

V0207_08_00_01_0.text: You think ya can smuggle anything past Sector Security?

V0207_08_00_01_1.text: I activate the Continuous Spell, Inspection!

V0207_08_00_02_0.text:
Time for your Inspection!
Show me your hand!

V0207_08_00_03_1.text: It negates a Trap and sends it back to the deck!

V0207_08_00_04_0.text: I activate my Continuous Trap, Greed!

V0207_08_00_05_1.text:
It's rainin' money!
Coins! Silver! Gold!
Cha-ching!

V0207_08_00_06_0.text: Before you attack, I'm investigating your hand!

V0207_08_00_06_1.text: I activate my Trap, The Forceful Checkpoint!

V0207_08_00_07_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Security Orb!

V0207_08_00_08_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Broken Blocker!

V0207_08_00_09_0.text: I activate the Trap, Regretful Rebirth!

V0207_08_00_10_0.text:
Hahaha! Caught ya!
My Counter Trap activates!
Intercept!

V0207_08_00_11_0.text:
Big mistake!
I activate the Trap, Sakuretsu Armor!

V0207_08_00_12_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Dust Tornado!

V0207_09_00_00_0.text: You destroyed Assault Dog, but my canine's effect activates!

V0207_09_00_00_1.text: I can whistle up more Assault Dogs from my deck!

V0207_09_00_01_1.text: Send the top three cards of your deck to the Graveyard!

V0207_09_00_02_1.text: You can't Special Summon this turn!

V0207_09_00_03_0.text: I'll use Goyo Guardian's effect to arrest ya!

V0207_09_00_04_0.text: Battle Gonogo and you switch to face-down Defense Position!

V0207_09_00_06_0.text: I'm usin' Samurai Sword Baron's effect!

V0207_09_00_08_0.text: Watch Jutte Fighter use its effect!

V0207_09_00_10_0.text:
I'll use Healing Wave Generator to restore my LP!
Starlight Wave!

V0207_09_00_10_1.text:
Oh yeah!
My strength's coming back!

V0207_09_00_12_0.text:
It's not over!
Stygian Sergeants is comin' right back at ya!

V0207_09_00_14_0.text: Handcuffs Dragon equips on to your monster and weakens it!

V0207_09_00_15_0.text: The equipped monster's a goner, but not my Handcuffs Dragon!

V0207_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0207_13_00_03_0.text: This'll change the outcome of this Duel!

V0207_13_00_09_0.text: Here's the Tuner Monster, Jutte Fighter!

V0207_13_00_10_0.text:
This'll track you down!
Pursuit Chaser!

V0207_13_00_15_0.text: Let's do this, Stygian Street Patrol!

V0207_13_00_16_0.text: I send these to the grave to Special Summon Montage Dragon!

V0207_13_00_16_1.text: And each monster gives 300 ATK per Level!

V0207_13_00_17_0.text:
This guy's the ticket!
Tactical Espionage Expert!

V0207_37_00_01_0.text: This monster will make you crash and burn!

V0207_13_00_19_0.text: Bow down to the ultimate authority figure!

V0207_37_00_03_0.text: This monster always gets his suspect!

V0207_37_00_04_0.text: Many have tried to escape, but all have failed!

V0207_13_00_22_0.text:
Level 3 Goyo Defender!
Reporting for duty!

V0207_37_00_05_0.text: To catch my prey, I call a predator!

V0207_19_00_00_0.text: Assault Dog! Bite a piece outta 'em!

V0207_19_00_20_0.text:
Goyo King!
Show 'em why you rule all!

V0207_21_00_00_0.text: The light's flashing red for YOU!

V0207_21_00_01_0.text: You can only avoid justice for so long!

V0207_21_00_02_0.text: How dare you toy with the law!

V0207_28_00_00_0.text:
Hahahaha!
Did you really think you could elude me?

V0207_28_00_01_0.text:
Too bad!
I knew every move you'd make!

V0207_28_00_02_0.text: I had you locked down from the start!

V0207_28_00_03_0.text: I swore to protect this city!

V0207_28_00_04_0.text: The citizens shouldn't rely on you hoodlums.

V0207_28_00_04_1.text: Not when they can count on me to protect New Domino City!

V0207_28_00_06_0.text: The citizens are under my protection!

V0207_28_00_06_1.text: So I won't let you drive around causing chaos!

V0207_28_00_07_0.text:
Did I impress you?
You must adore a man in uniform.

V0207_29_00_00_0.text:
I can't believe it...
I lost?!?

V0207_29_00_02_0.text: You may have outrun me today, but I'll catch you next time!

V0207_29_00_03_0.text:
Ergh...
This will not go unpunished!

V0207_29_00_04_0.text:
Yusei...
The day I met you was the day my life changed.

V0207_29_00_05_0.text:
Ahhhh! Noooo!
I should be faster than the Master of Faster!

V0207_29_00_06_0.text:
Rrrmp.
Kids grow up so quickly these days...

V0207_29_00_07_0.text:
Argh...
How can a kid speed through my strategies?

V0207_29_00_08_0.text: Heh, you're unexpectedly skilled for your age.

V0207_29_00_09_0.text: Security isn't permitted to lose against you...

V0207_29_00_10_0.text:
You're as tough as the law.
I like that.

V0207_33_00_01_0.text: Throw yourself to the mercy of the court!

V0207_34_00_03_0.text: Focus! You're still in a Duel!

V0207_34_00_04_0.text: C'mon, speak up! Cat got your tongue?

V0207_34_00_05_0.text: Let your cards do the talking!

V0207_34_00_06_0.text: Want to hire me as your personal bodyguard?

V0207_32_00_01_0.text: Witness the next generation of Dueling! Rev it up!

V0207_35_00_00_0.text: Our cards speak louder than words!

V0207_36_00_00_0.text: I got 'em trapped! Don't let 'em escape!

V0207_27_00_02_0.text: Wipe that smirk off your face!
